Helge app is for 13-19 y.o. students. Helge asks you questions about your wellbeing, analyzes the data, and provides real-time insight on how you are doing. If you wish to share your data with your school, then the data helps your teachers and school support specialists focus their solutions to the most pressing issues.

How does Helge work for students?
* Respond the regular test questions about well-being at school;
* Based on the test results get feedback and recommendations about their situation;
* If necessary, they may share their results with their school;
* If they wish, they can journal about their experiences, create tasks and explore new ideas.

Helge app can be used individually. However, it works best for you when your school has joined Helge programme. Get in touch with us to start testing in your school.

Check our Privacy Policy: https://helge.app/privacy-policy/

